  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/24/google-transportation-aware-shopping-patent/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/91bb60449e000f38c9705c553eb7f4ce/google-free-ride.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n亚马逊觉得「<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/18/amazon-anticipatory-shipping/\">预期发货</a>」很酷，但在 Google 眼中，还是把顾客带去商店里的做法比较好。他们在新专利中就基于该出发点发掘出了全新的促销模式：只要顾客想去广告主的商店，他们就会帮你省下相关的交通费用。当然，这并不代表说所有顾客都能享受到豪车待遇，Google 会根据每个人的信息（比如说位置、工作、购买记录等）来确定最终提供的交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n打个比方说，那些消费力较高的客户更可能得到 VIP 待遇，Google 说不定还会拿出<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2012/05/08/nevada-lets-googles-driverless-car-hits-the-open-road/\">自动驾驶车</a>来招待他们。至于普通消费者，拿到手的更可能是车票或出租车优惠。不过，说到底这个想法目前还只是专利，最终能否成真就要看 Google 怎么做啰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/24/google-transportation-aware-shopping-patent/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://news.slashdot.org/story/14/01/23/230212/should-self-driving-cars-chauffeur-shopping-whales-for-free\" target=\"_blank\">Slashdot</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&amp;Sect2=HITOFF&amp;d=PALL&amp;p=1&amp;u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsrchnum.htm&amp;r=1&amp;f=G&amp;l=50&amp;s1=8,630,897.PN.&amp;OS=PN/8,630,897&amp;RS=PN/8,630,897\" target=\"_blank\">USPTO</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/24/google-transportation-aware-shopping-patent/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20814921/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/24/google-transportation-aware-shopping-patent/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
